[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":966},["ShallowReactive",2],{"projets":3,"articles":345},[4,153,249],{"_path":5,"_dir":6,"_draft":7,"_partial":7,"_locale":8,"title":9,"description":8,"img":10,"project_type":11,"project_skills":12,"project_url":15,"readingTime":16,"body":21,"_type":147,"_id":148,"_source":149,"_file":150,"_stem":151,"_extension":152},"/projets/aeroport-nantes-atlantique","projets",false,"","Aéroport de Nantes Atlantique","aeroportnantes_homepage","Agence",[13,14],"Drupal","Multilingue","https://manitou.com/fr-FR",{"text":17,"minutes":18,"time":19,"words":20},"2 min read",1.54,92400,308,{"type":22,"children":23,"toc":144},"root",[24,42,109,124,133,139],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":27,"children":28},"element","project-header",{},[29],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":31,"children":32},"p",{},[33,36,40],{"type":34,"value":35},"text","Le groupe Manitou, fondé en 1957 et basé à Ancenis en France, est un leader mondial dans la conception et la fabrication de matériels de manutention, d'élévation de personnes et de terrassement. Manitou propose une large gamme de machines destinées aux secteurs de la construction, de l'agriculture et de l'industrie. En 2023, Manitou a réalisé un chiffre d'affaires de 2,9 milliards d'euros et employait 5 500 collaborateurs à travers le monde.",{"type":25,"tag":37,"props":38,"children":39},"br",{},[],{"type":34,"value":41},"\nNous avons été missionné en 2019 pour la refonte du site et depuis cette année là, nous continuons de développer des évolutions.",{"type":25,"tag":43,"props":44,"children":46},"block-steps",{"title":45},"Étapes du projet",[47,70,93],{"type":25,"tag":48,"props":49,"children":51},"block-step-item",{"title":50},"La co-construction",[52],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":53,"children":54},{},[55,57,60,62,68],{"type":34,"value":56},"La co-construction est une étape primordiale dans la création du projet. Elle permet de mettre autour de la table toutes les parties prenantes et de définir les besoins en accord avec les souhaits du client.",{"type":25,"tag":37,"props":58,"children":59},{},[],{"type":34,"value":61},"\nDans cette phase, ",{"type":25,"tag":63,"props":64,"children":65},"strong",{},[66],{"type":34,"value":67},"en tant que lead",{"type":34,"value":69},", j'ai pu vérifier la faisabilité des futurs développements.",{"type":25,"tag":48,"props":71,"children":73},{"title":72},"La phase de développement",[74],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":75,"children":76},{},[77,79,84,86,91],{"type":34,"value":78},"Pendant plusieurs mois, nous avons développé le site web. Mon rôle était de ",{"type":25,"tag":63,"props":80,"children":81},{},[82],{"type":34,"value":83},"mettre en place le socle du site",{"type":34,"value":85}," ainsi que ",{"type":25,"tag":63,"props":87,"children":88},{},[89],{"type":34,"value":90},"de leader et d'apporter du support aux autres développeurs",{"type":34,"value":92}," afin de mener à bien (et dans les temps) le projet.",{"type":25,"tag":48,"props":94,"children":96},{"title":95},"Maintenance et évolution",[97],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":98,"children":99},{},[100,102,107],{"type":34,"value":101},"Le site étant terminé, nous sommes rentrés dans une phase de maintenance. Manitou souhaitant être à la page sur les outils et process, nous avons eu la possibilité de mettre à jour et de développer des nouvelles fonctionnalités pour ",{"type":25,"tag":63,"props":103,"children":104},{},[105],{"type":34,"value":106},"permettre à Manitou de rester leader sur le marché",{"type":34,"value":108},".",{"type":25,"tag":110,"props":111,"children":113},"block-text",{"title":112},"Une mise en place du multilingue complexe !",[114,119],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":115,"children":116},{},[117],{"type":34,"value":118},"Manitou est un groupe internationnal et par conséquent le site web doit être accessible à l'ensemble des pays du monde entier. Nous avons donc mis en place un système de traduction par locale et actuellement, nous en avons plus d'une centaine ! De plus, des règles métiers sont venues complexifiées les développements.",{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":120,"children":121},{},[122],{"type":34,"value":123},"Nous avons également mis en place une synchronisation des différentes machines et accessoires qui ne sont pas forcément disponible pour l'ensemble des pays.",{"type":25,"tag":125,"props":126,"children":127},"block-title",{},[128],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":129,"children":130},{},[131],{"type":34,"value":132},"Quelques captures d'écran du site de Manitou :",{"type":25,"tag":134,"props":135,"children":138},"block-image",{"alt":136,"legend":136,"src":137},"Capture d'écran de la page \"Nos machines\", listant les différentes catégories de machines en France.","/img/projects/content/manitou_nos-machines_low.webp",[],{"type":25,"tag":134,"props":140,"children":143},{"alt":141,"legend":141,"src":142},"Capture d'écran du Store Locator du site de Manitou.","/img/projects/content/manitou_store-locator.png",[],{"title":8,"searchDepth":145,"depth":145,"links":146},2,[],"markdown","content:projets:aeroport-nantes-atlantique.md","content","projets/aeroport-nantes-atlantique.md","projets/aeroport-nantes-atlantique","md",{"_path":154,"_dir":6,"_draft":7,"_partial":7,"_locale":8,"title":155,"description":8,"img":156,"project_type":11,"project_skills":157,"project_url":15,"readingTime":158,"body":159,"_type":147,"_id":246,"_source":149,"_file":247,"_stem":248,"_extension":152},"/projets/artisans-artipole","Artisans Artipole","artipole_homepage",[13,14],{"text":17,"minutes":18,"time":19,"words":20},{"type":22,"children":160,"toc":244},[161,172,220,231,238,241],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":162,"children":163},{},[164],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":165,"children":166},{},[167,168,171],{"type":34,"value":35},{"type":25,"tag":37,"props":169,"children":170},{},[],{"type":34,"value":41},{"type":25,"tag":43,"props":173,"children":174},{"title":45},[175,191,208],{"type":25,"tag":48,"props":176,"children":177},{"title":50},[178],{"type":25,"tag":30,"props":179,"children":180},{},[